{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"selected","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"selected","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the view should display itself as selected; "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if it should display itself as unselected."}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" if the change in selection state is animated; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"change is immediate."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You should not call this method directly. A map view calls this method in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"response to user interactions with the annotation. Subclasses may override this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method in order to customize the appearance of the view depending on its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:"]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"setSelected:animated:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L230","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setSelected:animated:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"title":"setSelected:animated:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a custom annotation view"}],"role":"article","type":"topic","title":"Custom Annotation View","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"}}}